metadata.name: #01 Pride - Minnie meet Minnie
metadata.description:
#01 Pride - Minnie meet Minnie 

Dimensions : 3000 × 3000

This art collection is a promotion of self-affirmation, dignity and equality during pride month. 35% of this sale will be donated to The Trevor Project to help young LGBTQ+ people and help them navigate tough times and to prevent suicide.
